   <unorderedlist>
    <listitem><para>Layered approach to Application development.</para></listitem>
    <listitem><para>MVC architecture.</para></listitem>
    <listitem><para>Ajaxable pages, datalist, widgets.</para></listitem>
    <listitem><para>BusinessObjects - contains the business logic of the application.</para></listitem>
    <listitem><para>DataObjects - cached database rows</para></listitem>
    <listitem><para>Cacheable interface - caches pages, objects, widgets.</para></listitem>
